      "title": "COPE wants Audit on Litro Purchases",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The COPE Committee advised the Auditor-General to direct an investigation, on whether any irregularities have occurred in the purchase of gas.",
        "The Chairman of the COPE Professor Charitha Herath made the direction last night when the Chairman of Litro and the company\u2019s top management, as well as the former chairman were summoned to COPE.",
        "In the meantime, the COPE Committee questioned the Chairman of Litro Muditha Peiris regarding many issues including gas purchases.",
        "53 people arrested for illegal migration attempt; 2 smugglers also arrested",
        "Hirunika & several others arrested for protesting outside President\u2019s House"
